  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Rush Vagrant on Ubuntu14.04 LTS]]></title>
    <link href="http://woody1983.github.io/blog/2016/07/12/rush-vagrant-on-ubuntu14-dot-04-lts/"/>
    <updated>2016-07-12T06:33:38+00:00</updated>
    <id>http://woody1983.github.io/blog/2016/07/12/rush-vagrant-on-ubuntu14-dot-04-lts</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3>Installing Virtualbox &amp; Vagrant</h3>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="nv">$ </span>wget -q http://download.virtualbox.org/virtualbox/debian/oracle_vbox.asc
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$ </span>sudo apt-key add oracle_vbox.asc
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$ </span>sudo apt-get install virtualbox
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$ </span>sudo apt-get install vagrant
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Install the dkms package to ensure that the VirtualBox host kernel modules</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="nv">$ </span>sudo apt-get install virtualbox-dkms
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>Get First Vagrant Machine</h3>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="nv">$ </span>vagrant box add precise32 http://files.vagrantup.com/precise32.box
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$ </span>vagrant box add precise64 http://files.vagrantup.com/precise64.box
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>Configure Project</h3>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="nv">$ </span>mkdir vagrant_project
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">cd </span>vagrant_project
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$ </span>vagrant init
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>And Edit the <code>Vagrantfile</code> file</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'>config.vm.box <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;precise64&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c">#Synced Folder</span>
</span><span class='line'>config.vm.synced_folder <span class="s2">&quot;src/&quot;</span>, <span class="s2">&quot;/vagrant_data&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c">#Forward Port</span>
</span><span class='line'>config.vm.network <span class="s2">&quot;forwarded_port&quot;</span>, guest: 80, host: 8080
</span><span class='line'><span class="c">#Provision</span>
</span><span class='line'>config.vm.provision <span class="s2">&quot;shell&quot;</span>, path: <span class="s2">&quot;provision.sh&quot;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>Start Environment</h3>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'>~/vagrant_project_64<span class="nv">$ </span>vagrant up
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Shell Script</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>provision.sh</span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="c">#!/usr/bin/env bash</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nb">echo</span> <span class="s2">&quot;Installing Apache and setting apache up... please wait&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'>apt-get update &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;<span class="p">&amp;</span>1
</span><span class='line'>apt-get install -y apache2 &gt; /dev/null 2&gt;<span class="p">&amp;</span>1
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>rm -rf /var/www
</span><span class='line'>ln -fs /vagrant /var/www
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>

]]></content>
  </entry>
  
